title: Metrorun event: Auckland domain 5k fun run
description: This Sunday, we've organised a FREE fun run event with running heroes in the Auckland Domain to take the place of our regular long run. Those of you who are training for half and full marathon events may like to add some extra distance on! Meet in the Auckland domain by the museum at 0800 for an 0830 race start. The course takes in the bush trails of the Auckland domain (with a nice hill!), plus a bit of on-road and a bit of cross country. Register on Running heroes for the spot prizes.

title: Group trip: Rangitoto Island
description: This Sunday, we're running on Rangitoto Island in the Hauraki Gulf. This run is weather dependant, if the weather is not great, we'll be doing the Hobson Bay/Orakei loop instead. We'll catch the ferry over in the morning. The specific route will be posted on facebook along with details of sailing times and other important information.
